Flake8-SARIF
============

This is a plugin for Flake8 that will format the output as SARIF.


Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install flake8-sarif


Usage
-----

.. code-block:: bash

    flake8 --format=sarif ...


Competitors
-----------

None that I could find on PyPI


